21:57.465 --> 21:59.057
Go ahead, just--
-So, we can just--

21:59.233 --> 22:01.565
Yeah, bend over. Come on. I know.

22:01.736 --> 22:03.101
Just bend over.

22:03.270 --> 22:05.568
Excuse us for just a second.

22:07.808 --> 22:09.105
-Hit it softer. Yeah.
-Yeah!

22:09.276 --> 22:11.676
-Okay, all right, okay.
-Oh. Okay.

22:11.846 --> 22:14.144
-Not bad, huh? Go ahead, Jeffrey.
-Thank you, Mert.

22:14.315 --> 22:18.479
