22:18.652 --> 22:21.917
-Come on, Jeffrey. Show us how.
-Yes, Jeffrey, yes.

22:22.089 --> 22:24.182
Here you go, Jeffrey.

22:25.559 --> 22:28.426
Ah! Oh!

22:28.596 --> 22:30.291
-Jeffrey!
-Oh!

22:30.464 --> 22:32.329
-Nice shot.
-Hats off, Jeffrey.

22:32.500 --> 22:34.593
-Outstanding.
-Oh, my.

22:34.769 --> 22:39.934
