your best interest at heart.

24:54.708 --> 24:57.370
I suggest you break it off
with him via e-mail...

24:57.545 --> 24:59.979
...he may react violently
if you do it in person.

25:00.147 --> 25:03.344
Morning, gang.
-Hi, M-mert.

25:03.517 --> 25:04.848
What are you doing here?

25:06.353 --> 25:10.346
Uh.... Haven't you told him yet?

25:10.524 --> 25:13.391
-Told me what?
-Well....

25:14.295 --> 25:16.195
-Well....
-Well...

25:16.363 --> 25:20.493
...Jeffrey, your mother and I
have made a decision.

25:20.668 --> 25:22.363
You're never going
to see each other again?

25:23.737 --> 25:28.174
-No.
-No, no.

25:28.342 --> 25:31.368
No, no, no, sweetheart, no, no.

25:31.545 --> 25:35.606
Actually, what's happening is
that Mert is going to kind of like...

25:35.783 --> 25:39.776
...kind of, sort of move...

25:39.954 --> 25:42.149
...in, around the house a little bit,
you know?

25:42.323 --> 25:46.851
Kind of like on a temporary sort of--
Like sort of be here, and kind of--

25:47.027 --> 25:50.827
Oh, God.
Mert, move in. Like, with us, and....

25:51.532 --> 25:55.935
Well, we wanna....
We want to know how you feel.

25:56.770 --> 25:58.328
Jeffrey?

26:00.407 --> 26:02.500
Can I speak to you in private, please?

26:16.257 --> 26:17.383
Obviously you're upset.

26:17.558 --> 26:20.391
Of course I'm upset.
I wasn't even consulted, for Pete's sake.

26:20.561 --> 26:24.156
I'm so sorry. It's just that the last six weeks
have been a whirlwind and--

26:24.331 --> 26:26.424
What was all that
about you wanting my opinion?

26:26.600 --> 26:28.158
You don't care about what I think.

26:28.335 --> 26:30.565
Of course I care what you think,
you're my son.

26:30.738 --> 26:32.763
I love you more
than anything in the world...

26:32.940 --> 26:36.205
