26:45.152 --> 26:48.053
Fixed the sink.
The p-trap collar nut was loose.

26:48.656 --> 26:50.647
<i>It's two machines in one.</i>

26:50.824 --> 26:53.987
<i>Now for the first time ever
you can make homemade sausage...</i>

26:54.161 --> 26:58.063
<i>...and homemade pasta
as easy as one, two, three.</i>

27:04.338 --> 27:09.469
Look, I know we sprung this on you
a little bit abruptly...

27:09.643 --> 27:13.579
...so I don't blame you if you feel angry.
That's an authentic emotion.

27:13.747 --> 27:16.944
I encourage you
to go ahead and experience it.

27:17.951 --> 27:21.045
But just so you know...

27:21.221 --> 27:24.782
...I don't wanna
replace your father, and I.... Ha. Heh.

27:24.958 --> 27:27.518
I don't expect you to call me dad.

27:28.128 --> 27:33.998
But I do have one request,
and that is that you just give me a chance.

27:35.803 --> 27:37.828
You're a good kid, Jeffrey.

27:39.039 --> 27:41.030
I'd like to be your friend.

27:44.878 --> 27:46.505
You know...

27:47.648 --> 27:50.515
...only those who risk going too far...

27:50.684 --> 27:55.485
...can possibly find out
how far they can go.

27:56.490 --> 27:57.855
Hmm.

27:58.826 --> 28:00.726
I wrote that.

28:04.365 --> 28:05.662
Mitch, I need your help.

28:05.833 --> 28:08.233
Sorry, Jeffrey.
We stopped selling interactive porn.

28:08.402 --> 28:12.736
No. I want you to do some hacking for me.
His name is Merton Jacob Rosenbloom...

28:12.906 --> 28:15.898
...and I want all the dirt
you can dig up on him.

28:17.244 --> 28:19.940
-Fifty bucks.
-That's ridiculous.

28:20.114 --> 28:21.547
You're ridiculous.

28:26.820 --> 28:31.723
I'll give you 25 dollars
and a Warburtons discount card.

28:43.170 --> 28:46.162
Great choice, sir.
One of our most popular games.

28:46.340 --> 28:50.140
Good, good.
It's a gift for my girlfriend's son.

28:50.310 --> 28:53.211
-Cash or charge?
