you want to know.

29:12.733 --> 29:15.133
Really? What--? What is it?

29:31.552 --> 29:34.350
Hey! Hey!

29:34.521 --> 29:36.250
You remember me?

29:36.423 --> 29:38.323
-Remember?
-Oh, yeah.

29:38.492 --> 29:40.585
You want a ride?

29:40.761 --> 29:43.025
Yeah, then when I was like 17,
my dad was all:

29:43.197 --> 29:45.927
"Get rid of the tattoo
or get out of the house."

29:46.099 --> 29:48.932
So like, I've been on my own ever since.

29:50.471 --> 29:52.439
Why don't you have a car?

29:53.507 --> 29:56.738
I have severe carpal tunnel syndrome.

30:08.655 --> 30:11.419
Well, thanks for the ride.

30:11.592 --> 30:15.551
-It was nice of you.
-Actually, do you wanna get a beer?

30:16.864 --> 30:18.354
Um....

30:18.899 --> 30:22.027
My life's very complicated right now.

30:22.202 --> 30:25.399
