30:25.572 --> 30:29.099
Look, I appreciate the invitation...

30:29.276 --> 30:32.439
...but I think you should know
I'm seeing someone else.

30:32.613 --> 30:34.046
Her name's Allison.

30:35.582 --> 30:38.608
Whatever, you know. I just....

30:38.785 --> 30:40.878
Just trying to be nice.

30:41.088 --> 30:44.785
All right. Goodbye.

30:44.958 --> 30:46.983
Bye.

31:05.212 --> 31:07.646
The basement? Have you gone mad?

31:07.814 --> 31:10.044
