a night in that dank cave.

31:10.217 --> 31:12.447
You know how sensitive
my joints are to moisture.

31:12.619 --> 31:15.952
Now, it's perfectly dry down there,
and guess what. Guess what we did.

31:16.123 --> 31:20.219
We put in the old TV and VCR down there
so it's gonna be like your own bachelor pad.

31:20.394 --> 31:22.487
Honey? Oh, sweetheart.

31:22.663 --> 31:24.631
-Would you just please go away?
-Hey, buddy.

31:24.798 --> 31:26.959
Was this a great idea,
or was this a great idea?

31:27.134 --> 31:30.968
I was thinking the other night. You were
talking about how you didn't have privacy.

31:31.138 --> 31:32.162
That's when it hit me.

31:32.339 --> 31:35.797
I bet you can't wait to get to that basement
and start bringing in those ladies.

31:35.976 --> 31:37.967
-Ha-ha-ha.
-Oh, Mert. Oh.

31:38.879 --> 31:41.848
Here, take it.

31:42.015 --> 31:44.210
Take it, go on.

31:44.851 --> 31:49.754
It's just something from me to say
thank you for welcoming me to the family.

31:49.923 --> 31:51.481
-So sweet.
-Yeah.

31:51.658 --> 31:53.626
Well, open it, silly.

31:59.099 --> 32:01.329
-Oh, looky-look.
-But turn the--

32:01.501 --> 32:02.798
-Can I see that?
-Come on.

32:02.970 --> 32:04.369
What is it? What does it say?

32:04.538 --> 32:06.472
Ta-da! Ha-ha-ha.
Oh.

32:06.640 --> 32:09.803
You are now officially
a member of Team Rosenbloom.

32:13.246 --> 32:15.339
What do you say, Jeffrey? Jeffrey?

32:15.515 --> 32:16.982
<i>Please.</i>

32:17.884 --> 32:20.375
Thank you so much, Mert.

32:23.223 --> 32:25.350
You're welcome, buddy.

32:26.026 --> 32:27.357
-Whoo! Ha-ha-ha.
Ha-ha-ha.

32:27.527 --> 32:29.392
Scared you. Ha-ha-ha.

32:29.563 --> 32:30.996
Oh.

32:31.365 --> 32:34.528
I gotta tell you,
I got nothing on your boy. Diddlysquat.

32:34.701 --> 32:36.635
What? That's impossible.

32:36.803 --> 32:38.464
The Internet doesn't lie, bro.

32:38.639 --> 32:42.541
He's totally clean. Never been arrested,
no funny diseases, nothing.

32:44.177 --> 32:45.644
That's ridiculous.

32:46.780 --> 32:50.716
What do you think is more deviant?
Bondage or bestiality?

32:50.884 --> 32:52.909
<i>No, I don't know, dude.</i>

32:53.086 --> 32:54.553
<i>I haven't seen a boob in three years.</i>

32:55.922 --> 32:57.048
<i>It was at the pool.</i>

32:57.224 --> 32:58.851
Wait. Shh. Hold on.

32:59.493 --> 33:03.361
<i>She got out of the pool
and it just flopped out.</i>

33:16.009 --> 33:17.135
Oh, Mert. Oh!

33:17.310 --> 33:20.177
I'm having my way with you.
-No, they're headed for the bedroom.

33:21.982 --> 33:24.746
<i>Dude, what's going on?
Who's headed for the bedroom?</i>

33:24.918 --> 33:27.819
-Oh, Mert. Oh, Mert. Oh, honey.
-Oh! Oh!

33:27.988 --> 33:31.253
Your thighs are like a bear trap.
-Ugh!

33:31.425 --> 33:33.416
Oh.... Oh!

33:34.895 --> 33:36.692
<i>And everything's sponsored</i>

33:36.863 --> 33:38.888
<i>By huge corporations</i>

33:39.232 --> 33:43.896
<i>What will be next?
A Del Taco space station</i>

33:45.605 --> 33:49.666
<i>This corporate culture
Just sucks out our brains</i>

33:49.843 --> 33:55.076
<i>While the corporate vultures
Eat our remains</i>

33:56.383 --> 34:00.615
<i>From Wolfgang Pucks to Family Feud</i>

34:00.787 --> 34:05.190
<i>It all sucks and we're all screwed</i>

34:05.358 --> 34:09.317
<i>There's no way to escape</i>

34:09.663 --> 34:15.295
<i>From the corporate rape</i>

34:15.469 --> 34:20.371
<i>And this world that we're living in
