34:20.540 --> 34:24.636
<i>If you don't stop buying crap
At Staples and Baby Gap</i>

34:24.811 --> 34:30.340
<i>I'm an old-fashioned girl
And I'm stuck in a corporate world</i>

34:30.717 --> 34:34.880
<i>Hey, what can I say
I'm an old-fashioned girl</i>

34:35.054 --> 34:39.492
<i>That says screw this whole corporate world</i>

34:41.393 --> 34:42.418
<i>Yeah</i>

34:45.398 --> 34:48.993
-Whoo!
-Thank you, Skyler.

34:50.303 --> 34:52.828
-Well done.
-What are you doing here?

34:54.507 --> 34:55.770
Where's Allison?

34:55.942 --> 34:59.002
Actually, Allison and I just broke up.

34:59.179 --> 35:02.376
Long distance relationships
are impossible to maintain.

35:02.549 --> 35:04.517
I hear that.

35:04.684 --> 35:06.675
I guess I'll see you around.

35:06.853 --> 35:08.343
Wait a minute.

35:08.522 --> 35:11.685
I want to apologize
for being so brusque earlier.

35:12.526 --> 35:14.084
Whatever.

35:14.294 --> 35:16.387
