pilfer your lyrics off the Internet.

37:45.845 --> 37:49.110
-Screw you, dude.
-Jeffrey. Come on, let's get out of here.

37:52.018 --> 37:54.486
-You was a ho, anyway.
Oh! Ooh!

37:54.654 --> 37:56.519
