37:57.757 --> 37:58.951
What did you call her?

37:59.326 --> 38:01.590
I called her a bizznatch.

38:04.297 --> 38:05.662
Aah!

38:06.433 --> 38:08.833
-Oh!
-Ah! Trip!

38:09.002 --> 38:10.663
-Oh, oh.
Are you okay?

38:11.705 --> 38:13.138
